the kapil sharma show is an indian hindi stand-up comedy and talk show which premiered on 23 april 2016 and is broadcast by sony channel .   the series revolves around kapil sharma and his neighbors in the shantivan non co-operative housing society .   the series which was originally scheduled for 26 episodes , was later extended indefinitely .   development began in december 2015 , when sharma announced his plans to create a new show for a hindi general-entertainment channel other than colors tv .   it has received positive feedback from audiences , gaining top trps in the non-fiction category .